Taylor decided the revolution in Liberia or brought disasters to
the country, we should say he has won the election which means
total peace".
</P>
<P>
"As Liberians, it is our responsibility to embrace peace in
our country", she added.
</P>
<P>
All the refugees were looking forward to being back to the
country to rebuild their life, said the report.
</P>
<P>
the report did not say what move Guinea has taken to improve
its relations with Liberia.
</P>
<P>
It however warned the two countries should pay more attention
to their common borders which were sort of concern for both
during Liberia's civil war.  
