The city's large enterprises have played an important role in
raising foreign investment. The Longkou Conglin Group, for
example, has gotten 40 million US dollars in investment by selling
shares or setting up joint ventures. The group paid 120 million
yuan in taxes last year, ranking 22nd in China's top township
enterprises.
</P>
