trade fair was held recently in Shishi city in east China's Fujian
province.
</P>
<P>
A total of 450 million yuan in business was done at the fair,
which attracted over 400 textile and shoe companies from the
cities of Shanghai and Guangzhou, and from the Philippines,
Indonesia, Hong Kong, Taiwan, and other countries and regions.
</P>
