<HEADLINE> Pan Pacific Swimming Results (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, August 13 (Xinhua) -- Following are the final results at
the Pan Pacific swimming championships in Fukuoka, Japan, on
Wednesday:
</P>
<P>
Women's 200m individual medley
</P>
<P>
1. Kristine Quance, United States, 2:13.79
</P>
<P>
2. Marianne Limpert, Canada, 2:14.91
</P>
<P>
3. Joanne Malar, Canada, 2:16.17
</P>
<P>
4. Jennifer Parmenter, United States, 2:16.37
</P>
<P>
5. Chen Yan, China, 2:17.78
</P>
<P>
6. Yasuko Tajima, Japan, 2:18.08
