<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 13 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today rose 13 HK dollars today to close at 3,039 HK dollars a
tael, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in
Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 329.44 dollars a troy ounce, up
1.44 U.S. dollars at today's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar to
7.7435 HK dollars. 
</P>
</TEXT>
